The first time I met DC, he told me we’d be friends one day. 

Some 12 years later, I’m proud to call him one of my very best friends.

What an honor & joy it has been to do this show with him over the past year+. 

Thanks to all who watched and supported.

node.text:
Extremely excited to share that I will be a part of the @shosports broadcast team for next week’s @jakepaul x @twooodley card. They’ve assembled an amazing crew, and it’s a massive honor for me to be included. I’ll serve as a guest analyst during the fights and handle post-fight interviews. 

Very grateful and thankful to the whole @SHOsports team for this opportunity. It’s especially meaningful to me because I’ll be working with the legend, Canada’s own, Mauro Ranallo for the first time. Mauro has been a friend and mentor for over a decade, and I just can’t believe I finally get to work with the combat 🐐.

I grew up dreaming of opportunities like this. I played them out in my basement. To actually live them out now is surreal. This exact role. Truly surreal. Thank you all for your love and support in this new chapter. You guys give me so much strength and confidence, you have no idea. I hope the same for all of you. 🙏
